		-N show line numbers
		-~ do not show ~ after EOF
		+G tells less to start at the end of the file
		-F or --quit-if-one-screen
		v - opens editor defined in $VISUAL or $EDITOR
		:n - examine the next file
		<,> - go to home, end

EDIT:
tr - translate or delete characters (-d for delete)
