		-d ’:’ -f 1,7 /etc/passwd - only show the username and the shell
sort - sorts
	-u - uniq
	-t - set delimiter for fields (default is space)
	-k - select by which field to sort 
uniq - removes adjacent duplicates
	-d - intersection
	-u - difference
column - columnate text
	t - create a table
